songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Lean, Whitearmor
Lean, Lean
Two pills, two cups, two cups stuffed (Stuffed)
Two cups stuffed

[Verse 1]
She want me gone
Been here too long
Stacks up, gettin' high
'Bout to lose it, 'bout to lose it

[Chorus]
Two pills, two cups, two cups stuffed (Stuffed)
Rainbow, tangerine my blunt
Got my Margiela right, I don't pay none
I don't pay none, I feel like I'm the Pope

[Bridge]
You and me, not the same
These games you play
In my head all day
'Bout to lose it, 'bout to lose it, yeah
(Gone, gone on me
You gone, gone on me
You gone, gone on me
You gone)

[Chorus]
Two, two, two pills, two cups, two pills stuffed (Stuffed)
Two pills, two cups, two cups stuffed (Stuffed)
Rainbow, tangerine my blunt (Blunt)
Got my Margiela right, I don't pay none
I don't pay none, I feel like I'm the Pope

[Verse 2]
I don't pay none, I feel like I'm the Pope
Pop pills, running through the city in a scope
Scope and we blow and we smokin' on the dope
From the backstreets, yeah, you already know
I don't pay none, I feel like I'm the Pope
I don't pay none, I feel like I'm the Pope
I don't pay none, I feel like I'm the Pope

[Outro]
Pope, feel like I'm the Pope
Feel like I'm the Pope
Feel like I'm the Pope
songs.title: 2 Cups
